# Required for pushing published drafts to the terminal display (CIU265_IXDProject_Web / Supabase).
# Get from Supabase Dashboard -> Project Settings -> API -> service_role (server only, never commit).
# Server secret — pick ONE of these from Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API Keys:
#   • New: "Secret key"  → starts with sb_secret_
#   • Legacy tab: "service_role" → long JWT starting with eyJ...
# Do NOT use sb_publishable_... (that is only for CIU265_IXDProject_Web / browser).
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# Arduino typewriter button (close Arduino IDE Serial Monitor before npm start)
# SERIAL_PORT=COM8
# SERIAL_BAUD_RATE=9600

# Optional overrides (defaults are in data/terminalConfig.json)
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# TERMINAL_SESSION_ID=uuid-of-exhibition-session
